title: Halo Wars Definitive Edition RePack by BlackBox
description:
Halo Wars: Definitive Edition is an enhanced version of  the  real-
time strategy classic, Halo Wars, updated to run  natively  on  PC.
Set early in the iconic war between the Covenant and  UNSC  -  made
famous  by  the Halo  FPS games  - Halo  Wars:  Definitive  Edition
provides a unique angle on the war while bringing new heroes to the
battlefield. Control largeHaloarmies  and direct  them  in  action-
packed warfare.

Date: April 19, 2017
Genre: Strategy, Action,
Developer: Ensemble Studios, Behavior Interactive, 343 Industries
Publisher: Microsoft Studios
Lang: Russian, English
Activation: (CODEX)

System requirements:
Minimal:
OS: Windows 7 SP1 64-bit or higher
Processor: Intel Core i3 or Equivalent
Memory: 4 GB RAM
Graphics Card: Intel HD Graphics 4200 NVIDIA GeForce GT 740M AMD Radeon R5 M240
DirectX: Version 11
Disk space: 12 GB
